science/article/3253036/chinese-scientists-create-tiny-robot-could-help-treat-brain-aneurysms-and-tumours?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>栓塞是治疗这些危及生命的疾病的首选治疗方法之一，这些疾病每年导致超过 75 万人死亡。科学家表示，磁性“微纤维机器人”可以阻止血液供应，其盘绕形状比其他方法具有更多控制能力。</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Feb 2024 08:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3253036/chinese-scientists-create-tiny-robot-could-help-treat-brain-aneurysms-and-tumours?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>台湾海警的致命追捕能否被用来制定缓解两岸紧张局势的路线？</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3252954/could-fatal-taiwan-coastguard-chase-could-be-used-chart-course-ease-cross-strait-tensions?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>观察人士称，两名中国大陆渔民的死亡表明有必要开放与台湾的沟通渠道。</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Feb 2024 05:00:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3252954/could-fatal-taiwan-coastguard-chase-could-be-used-chart-course-ease-cross-strait-tensions?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>法律专家称，中国热门电影《二十条》是关于自卫权的“童话”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3253010/chinese-hit-film-article-20-fairy-tale-about-right-self-defence-legal-experts-say?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>顶尖电影人张艺谋的正当防卫新剧贺岁档爆满内地影院，但这现实吗？</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Feb 2024 02:00:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3253010/chinese-hit-film-article-20-fairy-tale-about-right-self-defence-legal-experts-say?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>OpenAI的Sora给中国的人工智能梦想泼了“冷水”，文本到视频的进步引发了更多的反省</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3253034/openais-sora-pours-cold-water-chinas-ai-dreams-text-video-advancements-prompt-more-soul-searching?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>Sora的推出迫使中国人工智能行业再次面临如何在美国制裁升级的情况下赶上最新技术的问题。</description><pubDate>Sat, 24 Feb 2024 00:00:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3253034/openais-sora-pours-cold-water-chinas-ai-dreams-text-video-advancements-prompt-more-soul-searching?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美国、欧盟忧虑加剧，中国1万亿元电动汽车、太阳能和电池出口面临产能过剩担忧</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3253000/chinas-1-trillion-yuan-ev-solar-and-battery-exports-face-overcapacity-concerns-us-eu-anxieties-grow?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>由于美国和欧盟的反倾销调查和关税扰乱了贸易，北京已经认识到产能过剩是 2024 年的主要挑战。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 22:00:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/global-economy/article/3253000/chinas-1-trillion-yuan-ev-solar-and-battery-exports-face-overcapacity-concerns-us-eu-anxieties-grow?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>世界战乱，中国坚守和平</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/world/article/3252809/world-engulfed-war-china-holding-out-peace?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>世界各地的许多冲突可以被视为一场新的、虽然分散的世界大战，其特点是政治不稳定、军费开支增加以及对传统冲突解决机制的信任下降。中国不想成为全球警察，而是致力于和平。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 21:30:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/comment/opinion/world/article/3252809/world-engulfed-war-china-holding-out-peace?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国大陆台湾高官承诺支持统一势力</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3253057/mainland-chinas-top-taiwan-official-pledges-support-pro-unification-forces?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中共四号人物王沪宁在一次会议上表示，官员们今年必须“推进统一进程”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 14:51:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3253057/mainland-chinas-top-taiwan-official-pledges-support-pro-unification-forces?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>小米推出主打摄影的14 Ultra智能手机，目标是在高端领域挑战苹果和华为</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3253041/xiaomi-unveils-photography-focused-14-ultra-smartphone-it-aims-take-apple-and-huawei-high-end?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>小米14 Ultra在高端智能手机市场的激烈竞争中上市，苹果和华为是主要竞争对手。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 14:30:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3253041/xiaomi-unveils-photography-focused-14-ultra-smartphone-it-aims-take-apple-and-huawei-high-end?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中美科技战：二线“传统芯片”处于半导体霸主之战的最前沿</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3253031/us-china-tech-war-second-tier-legacy-chips-forefront-battle-semiconductor-supremacy?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在尖端技术的竞争中，人们越来越认识到老一代芯片对于军事用途以及汽车和消费电子产品仍然至关重要。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 14:00:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3253031/us-china-tech-war-second-tier-legacy-chips-forefront-battle-semiconductor-supremacy?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>欧盟考虑经济安全措施之际，中国王毅敦促德国拒绝保护主义和“集团对抗”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3253045/chinas-wang-yi-urges-germany-reject-protectionism-and-bloc-confrontation-eu-eyes-economic-security?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在与德国外交政策顾问詹斯·普洛特纳会面时，中国高级外交官王毅呼吁柏林避免“去中国化”，因为布鲁塞尔计划加强外国投资审查并加强对向竞争对手出口技术的控制。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 13:04:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3253045/chinas-wang-yi-urges-germany-reject-protectionism-and-bloc-confrontation-eu-eyes-economic-security?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>辽宁舰甲板上首次看到中国歼35战斗机的野心</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3253044/fresh-sightings-chinas-j-35-fighter-plans-deck-liaoning-aircraft-carrier?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>分析师表示，该飞机仍处于开发阶段，必须能够处理滑跃跳跃和电磁弹射系统。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 13:02:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3253044/fresh-sightings-chinas-j-35-fighter-plans-deck-liaoning-aircraft-carrier?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>数百家中国企业因援助俄罗斯乌克兰战争而被美国制裁</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/world/united-states-canada/article/3253042/biden-imposes-500-new-sanctions-russia-so-putin-pays-steeper-price-ukraine-war-navalnys-death?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>500多项涉俄制裁名单中，有17家中国大陆或香港公司被点名；白宫表示，他们还希望让莫斯科对阿列克谢·纳瓦尔尼之死负责。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 12:54:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/world/united-states-canada/article/3253042/biden-imposes-500-new-sanctions-russia-so-putin-pays-steeper-price-ukraine-war-navalnys-death?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item></channel></rss>